            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="story-title">Amazing Course!</p>
        <p class="story-text">
          The rew are mantlury tisur business and ranpnt covin complentia to your instrol openizod roomse courserf. Then your Wealth Acceleraton Wealth Stasors!
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="story-card">
        <div class="story-user">
          <Image src={s2} alt="Student" class="story-av" />
          <div class="user-meta">
            <h4>Benily Hamer</h4>
            <div class="stars">
              <Star class="h-4 w-4 fill-yellow" />
              <Star class="h-4 w-4 fill-yellow" />
              <Star class="h-4 w-4 fill-yellow" />
              <Star class="h-4 w-4 fill-yellow" />
